titles.title: Hosanna, Hosanna, Hosanna in the Highest

verse.name: v1
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Hosanna, hosanna, hosanna in the highest Hosanna, hosanna, hosanna in the highest Lord, we lift up Your name With a heart full of praise We exalt You, O Lord our God Hosanna in the highest.{/lang-eng}

verse.name: v2
verse.lines: {lang-eng}Jesus, Jesus, Jesus is the Lord of lords Jesus, Jesus, Jesus is the Lord of lords Lord, we lift up Your name With a heart full of praise We exalt You, O Lord our God Hosanna in the highest.{/lang-eng}
